This map is made like the original Krusty Krab from the tv series Spongebob.
The Indoor of the Krusty Krab is allmost the same, i have made some custom props for it, with help from Gulli.

The map has 64 spawn points, secrets, cade rooms, iron curtains and jellyfish if you are bored.

###### Link to all models and prefabs i made for this map: [Models download on Gamebanana](http://www.gamebanana.com/prefabs/5818 "Models")


I hope you enjoy this submission my fellow zombie players. have fun!


thanks to www.firewallCS.net / *-=Leb=-
